{"type": "article", "id": 49506, "title": "历峰 100% 控股时尚电商 YNAP，以及，Dior 高定秀值得一看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-23T03:58:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47263, "name": "高定秀"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 47264, "name": "Paul Joe"}, {"id": 5522, "name": "历峰"}, {"id": 2710, "name": "A&F"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180123113807FJwE3OXgBQm91CyN.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-ynap-m-a-cmpne-financiere/richemont-bids-for-control-of-yoox-net-a-porter-as-luxury-expands-online-idUSKBN1FB0K9\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>历峰集团扩展奢侈品电商业务，28 亿欧元收购 YNAP</strong></a> | 历峰集团和时尚电商集团 YNAP 达成协议，将以每股 38 欧元的价格收购剩余的股份，溢价超过 26%。交易完成后，YNAP 的估值达到 53 亿欧元，并将从米兰证券交易所退市。YNAP 股东还将审议这项计划，不过 YNAP CEO Federico Marchetti 已经表示了支持。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/abercrombie-fitch-martinez-retirement-executive-chairman-hollister-q4-11120307/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 现任董事长即将退休，品牌第四季度业绩或超预期</strong></a> | 美国休闲服饰品牌 Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 日前发布声明表示，品牌第四季度的同店销售额将取得增长，消息发布后，A&amp;F 的股价大涨了 12%。另外，现任董事长 Arthur Martinez 将于 2 月 3 日退休，Terry L. Burman 接任。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>喜欢日本工艺品的话，将于 2 月 7 日至 9 日期间举办的<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-01-23/dainipponichi2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">“大日本市”</a>值得一看。 </p><p>这场展示会由有着 300 年历史的日本杂货品牌中川政七商店主办，自 2011 年创办以来，以促进日本工艺制作企业间的交流为目的，对外推广地域工艺品。今年的这届展会将会有 52 家公司的 59 个品牌参展。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123112932yT5Pbi6awLZdt1FS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.509091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231129319YFvrukSKjqeU3Bh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123112933acVgDGsI4wSU0AJX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123112933PqMJBvDcGpyf6ZEL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123112933WoSJdURy4sFMcnBQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231129335CZwgR0k2b1qxP6T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.675758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>金·卡戴珊将在 2 月 1 日在自己的网站 kkwfragrance.com 上推出全新的香水系列 <a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/kim-kardashian-kkw-kimoji-heart-fragrances\" rel=\"nofollow\">kimoji 心形香水</a>。目前该系列的香型还未公布，不过已经可以看到香水的造型了，像糖果一样的心形。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123112958y6s7NYpImOCcLWkR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>法国时尚品牌 PAUL &amp; JOE 的文具系列 <a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-01-19/pauljoe-papeterie-2018ss/\" rel=\"nofollow\">La Papeterie </a>发布了 2018 春夏系列新品，效果依然很少女心，有包包、文件夹、手帐、零钱包，还有手机壳、胶带、信笺等小物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113019ldRoHLsVSC8WAJuM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.580303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113021uWVSvwU5Xq4D16a2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113021dCPEO3eWY7S8Zyt6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113021drnDF512XouLYcks.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113021E3jyQ9oWBaNTF4tU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113021CuvULSgDs6xeYOMy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上周末，美国设计师品牌<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/thom-browne-fw18/#slide-18\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Thom Browne </a>在巴黎发布了 2018 秋冬系列。这一季男装里，所有的模特都梳着长辫子，打上了红扑扑的腮红，扎着品牌标志性的红蓝色蝴蝶结，居然还蛮可爱的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113054C8ShUNDRZFVq6pHa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113057uZfY1V5hmw7T6Uce.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231130576SRs4MjVK2AJb7TP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113058HUBrdy25QiAKwmWh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113058muHwG2dYBWgbQRri.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113058dBtVswjxXg02aAFC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113059W3jyH7JBA4D8Zeh2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113101VQFAgn8c4PMDKZ9X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113102jPnJqUE78DYSVfgM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113102ZMdbV8jtA9uhHI1Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113102KYVb14OGfx320McZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113103V46Pfs7yCwSrlYQJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113103pY1nMCKcbBxEawNm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231131049dByOHDSZYvGMuh4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113105w3K5p7UFfLXMBxao.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231131069wUIsGrtV0na5h47.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113107l64vA271neifzcIX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113108Tuz59n6ZK17qdhaW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113108biBQrlMgE6tCWsLH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113109MlAaF5X2gcVrobDv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113109iagFfju98xbcAIOS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113109rMxfWEi8YCsTylg0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎高定时装周开始了，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/spring-couture-2018/paris/christian-dior/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior </a>在巴黎罗丹博物馆开场。</p><p>这场秀相当梦幻，设计师 Maria Grazia Chiuri 以超现实主义和离经叛道的女性艺术家 Leonor Fini 为灵感。 在天花板上悬挂着超现实主义的雕塑，如嘴巴、鼻子和耳朵，还有抛光的黑色鸟笼。</p><p>这一季的 look 有很多的薄纱和抽象几何元素，有的模特还戴起了面纱和面具，又前卫又神秘。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113521TUfm8y4uitLwFYn0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113212KNUdXuxlpyAHcvDF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113214hUunbZI4p2lJXgFz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113215odhCGKOVnLaW5EJp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113216AVRUTfsxCNEnuBSk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231132175AfI2ZaGRvhjmSk4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113219eL2dF1GvmsqrUlXt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113219rdAVNLTUzsybcPpR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113220eETHPSNjcwAdkbZJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113220P8Dk2O7Bgfp9uNz1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113220pdiOAyWxn4hI2PMo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113223PosrSNIKUfROEluJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231132244imO1h9YoB8FIPar.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113224SncHVxqLlZ2Qj4oK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113224ZMfaAv7tEpFJOK4y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113224JO4mKUwtyFAdTc7j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113226VDCaGHJBsSmU7e2t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231132263tL2PQAomapVsKyN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113228E4HpxV6ikmdIynlr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113229KiOn2hZC0UQgMIea.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231132292TYW4pzn60fqK9dN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113231IiAcUNzsOwjVp24D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113231uDmJ4vxZRzPe0sjO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113233OcaAC4Zy1FodrIxP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113233W8DOBnxop9Jsjzvh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113234T0KhjFgs718ZPkQt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123113234QkDtKiAp9gvI24Wm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801231132342vDOX6iSeb